  39:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         You can also configure the RTC Wakeup timer in interrupt mode using the
  40:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         HAL_RTCEx_SetWakeUpTimer_IT() function.
  41:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC Wakeup Counter register, use the HAL_RTCEx_GetWakeUpTimer()
  42:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
  43:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
  44:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *** Timestamp configuration ***
  45:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   ===============================
  46:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
  47:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To configure the RTC Timestamp use the HAL_RTCEx_SetTimeStamp() function.
  48:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         You can also configure the RTC Timestamp with interrupt mode using the
  49:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         HAL_RTCEx_SetTimeStamp_IT() function.
  50:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC Timestamp Time and Date register, use the
  51:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         HAL_RTCEx_GetTimeStamp() function.
  52:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) The Timestamp alternate function is mapped to RTC_AF1 (PC13).
  53:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
  54:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *** Internal Timestamp configuration ***
  55:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   ===============================
