  57:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To enable the RTC internal Timestamp use the HAL_RTCEx_SetInternalTimeStamp()
  58:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
  59:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC Timestamp Time and Date register, use the HAL_RTCEx_GetTimeStamp()
  60:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
  61:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
  62:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *** Tamper configuration ***
  63:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   ============================
  64:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
  65:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To enable the RTC Tamper and configure the Tamper filter count, trigger
  66:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         Edge or Level according to the Tamper filter value (if equal to 0 Edge
  67:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         else Level), sampling frequency, NoErase, MaskFlag, precharge or
  68:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         discharge and Pull-UP use the HAL_RTCEx_SetTamper() function.
  69:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         You can configure RTC Tamper in interrupt mode using HAL_RTCEx_SetTamper_IT()
  70:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
  71:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) The default configuration of the Tamper erases the backup registers.
  72:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         To avoid this, enable the NoErase field on the RTC_TAMPCR register.
  73:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) The TAMPER1 alternate function is mapped to RTC_AF1 (PC13).
  74:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) The TAMPER2 alternate function is mapped to RTC_AF2 (PA0).
  75:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) The TAMPER3 alternate function is mapped to RTC_AF3 (PC12).
  76:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c **** 
  77:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *** Backup Data Registers configuration ***
