  79:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   [..]
  80:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To write to the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPWrite()
  81:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
  82:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****     (+) To read the RTC Backup Data registers, use the HAL_RTCEx_BKUPRead()
  83:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****         function.
