 158:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Sets Timestamp.
 159:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note   This API must be called before enabling the Timestamp feature.
 160:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  hrtc pointer to a RTC_HandleTypeDef structure that contains
 161:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                the configuration information for RTC.
 162:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampEdge Specifies the pin edge on which the Timestamp is
 163:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         activated.
 164:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 165:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_RISING: the Timestamp event occurs on
 166:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        the rising edge of the related pin.
 167:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPEDGE_FALLING: the Timestamp event occurs on
 168:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *                                        the falling edge of the related pin.
 169:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampPin Specifies the RTC Timestamp Pin.
 170:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
 171:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_TIMESTAMPPIN_DEFAULT: PC13 is selected as RTC Timestamp Pin.
 172:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @note Although unused, parameter RTC_TimeStampPin has been kept for portability
 173:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *       reasons.
