 232:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   * @param  RTC_TimeStampEdge Specifies the pin edge on which the Timestamp is
 233:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *         activated.
