1625:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PLUSPULSES_SET: Add one RTCCLK pulse every 2*11 pulses.
1626:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_rtc_ex.c ****   *             @arg RTC_SMOOTHCALIB_PLUSPULSES_RESET: No RTCCLK pulses are added.
